name: 🦇 KALONG NEFERTITI 🦇
description:
Series of "TABIAT" 

Reflect the behavior and alay phenomena of my own daily life in Jakarta.
divides itself into three human characters who have an interest in food such as cilok (a cheap version of meatballs), egg rolls and narcissistic behavior, as well as make-up that seems far-fetched and cannot be accepted by society.

This illustration is a digital version of manual embroidery

I dedicate "KALONG NEFERTITI" 
(Kalong is Bat)

-2019-
